{"tid":1880234,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情人節，同男朋友上床，但係未扑野佢就嬲左我","createTime":"2020-02-14T16:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T17:47:23.000Z","uid":35361,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2135f33b71bab1ff1c71d18bf88df2ba6bd8d5c1","tid":1880234,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:41:22.000Z","msg":"今日去左男朋友屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢屋企冇人, 緊係要大戰連場啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家好快手就除哂衫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢又摷下我, 我又咀下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大家都摷到high哂, 佢又扯到恆哂 準備埋牙之制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁佢諗住入我先, 但我當時話 : 我依家都硬哂喎, 次次都係你入先, 不如今次我入你先 比我出一獲先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢即時黑面話我唔理佢感受, 只顧自己出野 果晚大家不歡而散 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實大家都扯到硬哂, 邊個入先會好D?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160459817b81ec7011365400a7a2b4312e169986","tid":1880234,"uid":239655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e3b66533e965106028464072e5bd3fcfb39756","tid":1880234,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-1